[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]What is ItemMagnet?[/B][/SIZE]

ItemMagnet adds [B]craftable tiered magnet tools[/B] that pull nearby dropped items toward the player with [B]visible, line-of-sight physics[/B] — items slide around corners and stop at walls instead of teleporting through blocks.

Charge your resonator with [B]redstone dust[/B] (sneak + right-click, either hand) or let it [B]auto-absorb[/B] redstone from the ground. [B]Redstone blocks[/B] trigger a [B]power surge[/B]: extra charge plus a temporary radius boost shown on the item lore.

Built for survival SMPs that need [B]Lands[/B], [B]WorldGuard[/B], [B]Towny[/B], and [B]GriefPrevention[/B] respect out of the box — with an [B]in-game config GUI[/B], presets, unlock gates, and a developer API.

[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]Highlights[/B][/SIZE]

[LIST]
[*][B]Three tiers[/B] — Fragment, Survey, Anchor (fully configurable materials, names, radius, drain)
[*][B]Live item lore[/B] — charge, boost timer, and current pull radius update in real time
[*][B]Hold modes[/B] — main hand, any hotbar slot, or anywhere in inventory (passive magnet)
[*][B]XP orb pulling[/B] — optional experience orb collection at the same radius
[*][B]Redstone fuel loop[/B] — dust recharge, block power surge, per-fuel sounds
[*][B]Claim-aware[/B] — Lands wilderness/owner/member/flag modes; WG regions; Towny; GP
[*][B]In-game config GUI[/B] — [CODE]/itemmagnet config[/CODE] for settings, tiers, fuel, integrations
[*][B]Rename items[/B] — change tier display names from the GUI (chat input, color codes)
[*][B]Unlock gates[/B] — permission, advancement, CMI stat/rank, or admin command (persisted)
[*][B]Anti-AFK[/B] — optional movement check with one-time notify (no spam)
[*][B]PlaceholderAPI[/B] — charge, radius, tier, boost placeholders
[*][B]Developer API[/B] — cancellable pull, fuel absorb, deplete, and XP pull events
[/LIST]

[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]How it plays[/B][/SIZE]

[LIST=1]
[*]Unlock or craft a tier resonator (Fragment → Survey → Anchor)
[*]Hold the magnet (main hand, hotbar, or inventory — your choice)
[*]Fuel with redstone dust (sneak + right-click) or pick up redstone drops
[*]Drop items nearby — they [B]slide[/B] toward you with particles and optional arm swing
[*]Use a redstone block for a [B]power surge[/B] — bigger radius for a limited time
[*]Magnets respect claim borders — pull stops at Lands/WG/Towny/GP boundaries
[/LIST]

[I]Tip: Run [CODE]/itemmagnet debug[/CODE] to see your active magnet's tier, charge, radius, and protection state.[/I]

[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]Commands[/B][/SIZE]

[TABLE]
[TR][TH]Command[/TH][TH]Permission[/TH][TH]Description[/TH][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet[/TD][TD]—[/TD][TD]Show help (filtered by permission)[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet reload[/TD][TD]itemmagnet.reload[/TD][TD]Reload config and messages[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet config[/TD][TD]itemmagnet.config[/TD][TD]Open in-game config editor[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet version[/TD][TD]itemmagnet.admin[/TD][TD]Version and hook status[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet give <player> <tier|all> [charge][/TD][TD]itemmagnet.give[/TD][TD]Give a resonator[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet giveall <player> [charge][/TD][TD]itemmagnet.give[/TD][TD]Give all tiers[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet unlock <player> <tier|all>[/TD][TD]itemmagnet.unlock[/TD][TD]Unlock a recipe[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet unlockall <player>[/TD][TD]itemmagnet.unlock[/TD][TD]Unlock all recipes[/TD][/TR]
[TR][TD]/itemmagnet debug[/TD][TD]itemmagnet.debug[/TD][TD]Stats for your active magnet[/TD][/TR]
[/TABLE]

Aliases: [CODE]/im[/CODE], [CODE]/magnet[/CODE]

[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]Permissions[/B][/SIZE]

[LIST]
[*][B]itemmagnet.use[/B] (default: true) — use magnets
[*][B]itemmagnet.use.<tier>[/B] (default: true) — per-tier use (fragment, survey, anchor)
[*][B]itemmagnet.wilderness[/B] (default: op) — use in Lands/Towny wilderness
[*][B]itemmagnet.bypass.lands[/B] — skip Lands checks
[*][B]itemmagnet.bypass.regions[/B] — skip WorldGuard region lists
[*][B]itemmagnet.admin[/B] (default: op) — reload, give, unlock, config, version
[/LIST]

Full list: [URL='https://github.com/RMHavelaar101/item-magent/blob/main/docs/permissions.md']Permissions docs[/URL]

[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]Configuration[/B][/SIZE]

On first run, edit [CODE]plugins/ItemMagnet/config.yml[/CODE] or use [CODE]/itemmagnet config[/CODE].

Key sections:
[LIST]
[*][B]tiers[/B] — materials, display names, lore, radius, recipes, unlocks, whitelists
[*][B]fuel[/B] — dust vs block charge, power surge, per-fuel sounds
[*][B]integrations[/B] — Lands, WorldGuard, Towny, GriefPrevention
[*][B]settings[/B] — hold-mode, sounds, XP pull, fuel radius, arm swing
[*][B]anti-afk[/B] — movement requirement, notify-once
[*][B]height[/B] — underground vs surface radius modifier
[*][B]presets[/B] — [CODE]theryn[/CODE], [CODE]testing[/CODE], or custom
[/LIST]

Most settings hot-reload with [CODE]/itemmagnet reload[/CODE]. Metrics keys may need a restart (plugin warns you).

Full docs & support: [URL='https://itemmagnet.theryn.org']itemmagnet.theryn.org[/URL]
Configuration: [URL='https://github.com/RMHavelaar101/item-magent/blob/main/docs/configuration.md']Configuration docs[/URL]
Config GUI: [URL='https://github.com/RMHavelaar101/item-magent/blob/main/docs/config-gui.md']Config GUI guide[/URL]

[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]Integrations[/B][/SIZE]

[LIST]
[*][B]Lands[/B] — wilderness, owner, member, flag-based modes
[*][B]WorldGuard[/B] — region whitelist/blacklist, item-pickup flag
[*][B]Towny[/B] — town plot protection
[*][B]GriefPrevention[/B] — claim respect
[*][B]PlaceholderAPI[/B] — [CODE]%itemmagnet_charge%[/CODE], [CODE]%itemmagnet_radius%[/CODE], tier, boost
[*][B]CMI[/B] — stat/rank unlock gates
[/LIST]

All integrations are optional — the plugin runs standalone.

